Sprintly-Beta (Agile development and workflow platform)
=======================================================

Sprintly is an agile development and workflow platform designed to help teams manage their projects efficiently. It provides tools for planning, tracking, and collaborating on software development projects, making it easier for teams to stay organized and deliver high-quality products.


Setup Instructons
-----------------

1] npx create-next-app sprintly-beta
2] cd sprintly-beta
3] npx shadcn@latest init
    -> npx shadcn@latest add button accordion avatar badge card carousel dialog drawer input popover select sonner tabs textarea
    -> npm install next-themes
4] npm install @clerk/nextjs
5] npm i @clerk/themes
6] npm install embla-carousel-autoplay
7] npm i -D prisma
8] npx prisma init
9] npx prisma generate
10] npx prisma migrate dev
11] npm i react-spinners
12] npm install date-fns
13] npm install @uiw/react-md-editor
14] npm i react-hook-form zod @hookform/resolvers